author: Dalevon Gallashaw (Published Photographer)
title: Dalevon Gallashaw (Published Photographer)
text: I was nervous to purchase at first. I got a Iphone 6s Plus 128 like new for a mind blowing deal on offerup, the person told me it was unlocked and of course it wasn't it was locked to AT&T and with payments. I was mad so I found this site from Google and paid the $28 but I needed the premium because it had a unpaid balance (payments). So I had to pay a additional $59. Paid it and waited, I watched the tracking first it said sent to unlock server then sent to supplier after that my phone was unlocked after I got the email im so happy now. I paid the $28 on Friday then the $59 on Sunday and it was unlocked on Thursday. It took about a week but I can use my phone. You can trust these guys I will purchase again. Thank you
